text: The Château de Fromental is an historic château in Fromental, Haute-Vienne, France. It was built in the 17th century. It has been listed as an official historical monument since June 8, 1925. ==References== Category:Châteaux in Haute-Vienne Category:Monuments historiques of Nouvelle-Aquitaine Category:Houses completed in the 17th century
title: Château de Fromental
